data-exc=""><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">However, there was one big problem. The distance between Malibu and B-town was enormous! It takes </span><span style="text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(254, 67, 151);"><strong>33</strong></span><span style="text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> hours to fly from one place to the other. They couldn't just jump on a scooter or ride a magical unicorn to meet each other. </span><span style="text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt; white-space: pre-wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">After six months of talking every day, Britney had an idea, she bravely asked Kenny if he wanted to move in together. It was not just a </span><span style="text-decoration: underline; color: rgb(254, 67, 151);"><span style="font-weight: bold;">weekend </span><strong>getaway</strong></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">, it was a big decision and Kenny needed some time to think about it.</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt; white-space: pre-wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br></span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt; white-space: pre-wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Weeks passed, and Britney anxiously waited for Kenny's answer. She wondered if he felt the same way about their love, and if they could find a way to be together. But no matter how much she checked her phone, no message from Kenny arrived. Little did Britney know, Kenny was going through a remarkable transformation inside his heart. He realized that Britney was the one he wanted to be with forever. So, he decided to do something special to surprise her.</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt; white-space: pre-wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br></span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14px; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: left; color: rgb(35, 35, 35); line-height: 1.38;"><span style="text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Kenny took a cute selfie while holding a </span><span style="text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(254, 67, 151); font-weight: bold;">coconut</span><span style="text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> drink </span><span style="text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">on the beach and got it printed as a postcard. He grabbed a pen and wrote a romantic message to Britney. He told her how much he loved her and that he had booked a flight for her to come to Malibu. With excitement bubbling inside him, Kenny sent the postcard on its way. </span><span style="text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt; white-space: pre-wrap;">Sadly, on its journey to B-town, the postcard encountered a little hiccup. There was a delivery issue, and poor Britney never received the card! She didn't know about Kenny's grand gesture and his plan to bring her to Malibu.</span><br></p><p style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: left; color: rgb(35, 35, 35);"><span style="caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14px; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: left; color: rgb(35, 35, 35); line-height: 1.38;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Can you help Britney to get to Kenny?!</span></p></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1689764653859" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1689764653859" data-extraclass="" data-layout-lg="4+4+4" data-layout-md="4+4+4" data-layout-sm="4+4+4" data-layout-xs="12+12+12"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-4 gf_col-md-4 gf_col-xs-12 gf_col-sm-4" id="c-1689764549317" data-id="1689764549317"><div data-la